data.description: Beautiful all brick home in Epernay w/ views of Pinnacle Mountain!  4bdrm, 3 full baths, 3117 sqft! Kitchen is open to living room and another dining area. granite CT's , island, double oven. Large Walk in pantry w/electrical outlets for appliances.  Family room has brick fireplace and built ins. Large walk in pantry w/ electrical outlets. Master suite has coffered ceilings and door to the covered deck.  Soaker tub, double vanity, walk in shower, walk in closet w/built ins. Formal Dining Room and Office.  Upstairs 2 bedrooms w/ walk in closets. Huge floored attic that is amazing for storage! Fully Fenced yard & more storage under house. New blinds & Plantation Shutters! Come See!
